'''紅石電路'''是指利用《[[Minecraft|Minecraft]]》遊戲中的一個虛構資源'''紅石'''所創作的衍伸作品。在《[[Minecraft|Minecraft]]》遊戲中，'''紅石'''被設計成可以產生出與傳遞一種名為紅石的[[能量|能量]]，具備可以製作成有如現實中的[[電子零件|電子零件]]的特性，並可以利用這個資源來完成各種[[機械|機械]][[裝置|裝置]]及[[機關|機關]]，還可以做出[[邏輯閘|邏輯閘]]和[[電腦|電腦]]<ref name="RedstoneComputer">{{cite web |url=http://www.escapistmagazine.com/news/view/104029-Player-Creates-Working-Computer-in-Minecraft |title=Player Creates Working Computer in ''Minecraft'' |work=[[The_Escapist_(magazine)|The Escapist]] |publisher=Alloy Digital |last=Tito |first=Greg |date=October 4, 2010 |accessdate=January 4, 2011 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101008064435/http://www.escapistmagazine.com/news/view/104029-Player-Creates-Working-Computer-in-Minecraft |archive-date=2010-10-08 |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://mt.sohu.com/20160420/n445212508.shtml |title=《我的世界》红石电脑制作原理及使用教程 |publisher=搜狐 |archive-url=https://archive.today/20181013083310/http://www.sohu.com/a/70507442_119573 |archive-date=2018-10-13 |dead-url=no |date=2016-04-20 |accessdate=2018-10-13 }}{{Wayback|url=http://mt.sohu.com/20160420/n445212508.shtml |date=20170119050900 }}</ref>，甚至還可以製作出改變遊戲體驗的[[系統|系統]]，但不如[[Minecraft模組|Minecraft模組]]方便。紅石被認為賦予《Minecraft》遊戲深度的一個物件。由於《Minecraft》的流行，紅石電路也經常被用作於[[電子學|電子學]]與數位[[邏輯電路|邏輯電路]]的入門教材<ref name="learn" />，也使《Minecraft》成為許多研究的主題<ref>{{cite thesis |url=http://140.113.214.176/~learninglab/paper_master/Research%20on%20the%20Relationship%20among%20Construction%20Games,%20Spatial%20.pdf |title=Research on the Relationship among Construction Games, Spatial Ability, and Reconstruction Ability |publisher=[[國立交通大學|國立交通大學]] |work=Institute of Multimedia Engineering, College of Computer Science |first=Cheng-You |last=Tsai |date=August 19, 2014 |accessdate=March 9, 2016 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160313022850/http://140.113.214.176/~learninglab/paper_master/Research%20on%20the%20Relationship%20among%20Construction%20Games,%20Spatial%20.pdf |archive-date=2016-03-13 |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref name="twvs.tnc" /><ref name="Tom_Peerdeman_UVA1" />，紅石可以視為賦予《Minecraft》遊戲深度、在其他相似遊戲脫穎而出，並讓遊戲性達到飛躍的關鍵要素<ref>{{cite web | title=如何做一款賺錢的沙盒手遊？ :5.紅石機關 | url=http://youxiputao.tw/articles/5177 | publisher=遊戲葡萄 | archive-url=https://archive.today/20160316165127/http://youxiputao.tw/articles/5177 | archive-date=2016-03-16 | dead-url=yes | date=2015-09-28 | accessdate=2016-01-27 }}</ref>。

== 紅石 ==
'''紅石'''是《[[Minecraft|Minecraft]]》遊戲中的一個虛構資源，是組成紅石電路的一個重要元素。在遊戲中，紅石是一種[[紅色|紅色]]的[[礦物|礦物]]，開採或精煉後可獲得紅石粉<ref>{{Cite web | author = Cale Hunt | url = https://www.windowscentral.com/beginners-guide-redstone-minecraft-windows-10-edition | publisher = Windows Central | title = Beginner's guide to redstone in Minecraft | date = 2016-11-12 | accessdate = 2018-10-19 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20181020053040/https://www.windowscentral.com/beginners-guide-redstone-minecraft-windows-10-edition | archive-date = 2018-10-20 | dead-url = no }}</ref>，在遊戲中是利用紅石粉鋪設紅石電路或加工成其他電子元件<ref name="npr.org">{{Cite web | title = 'Schoolifying' Minecraft Without Ruining It | author = Anya Kamenetz | date = 2017-08-09 | url = https://www.npr.org/sections/ed/2017/08/09/539518179/schoolifying-minecraft-without-ruining-it | website = npr.org | quote = The Minecraft material "redstone," which simulates electrical circuits | access-date = 2019-09-08 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190612225643/https://www.npr.org/sections/ed/2017/08/09/539518179/schoolifying-minecraft-without-ruining-it | archive-date = 2019-06-12 | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web | url = https://www.theguardian.com/technology/2015/jul/05/whats-next-for-minecraft-mojang-future-features-minecon-2015 | title = What's next for Minecraft? Developer Mojang talks future features | quote = redstone can be dropped as dust to create circuits that transmit power | date = 2015-07-05 | website = theguardian.com | access-date = 2019-09-08 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190407030537/https://www.theguardian.com/technology/2015/jul/05/whats-next-for-minecraft-mojang-future-features-minecon-2015 | archive-date = 2019-04-07 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

== 歷史 ==
雖然《我的世界》的第一個[[个人电脑|PC]]版於2009年五月中旬發布<ref name="PcGamerFirstMoments">{{cite web |url=http://www.pcgamer.com/the-first-moments-of-minecraft/ |title=The First Moments of Minecraft |author=Graham Smith |date=6 February 2012 |publisher=Future plc |work=PC Gamer |accessdate=12 February 2016 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160310072221/http://www.pcgamer.com/the-first-moments-of-minecraft/ |archive-date=2016-03-10 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，但當時遊戲中並不包含任何可以製作機關的系統，直到2010年中發布alpha版時官方加入了紅石，起初僅是為了能讓遊戲可以做出機關<ref name="Donnie_R."/>，後來才許多玩家紛紛利用這個特性做出了[[電路|電路]]或與數位邏輯<ref name="twvs.tnc"/>。

早在2010年時，《Minecraft》的作者[[馬庫斯·阿列克謝·泊松|馬庫斯·阿列克謝·泊松]]（Notch）就已經有為遊戲加入可製作機關的打算。2010年1月，泊松在早期的版本加入了齒輪{{#tag:ref|Donnie R. Minecraft: A History, Pioneer School, 2014<ref name="Donnie_R.">{{cite web |url=http://www.pioneerschools.org/cms/lib/NY19000288/Centricity/Domain/208/Pioneer_Newspaper%20April%202014%20-%20website.pdf |title=Pioneer Central Schools News |publisher=Pioneer School |accessdate=March 9, 2016 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160313202842/http://www.pioneerschools.org/cms/lib/NY19000288/Centricity/Domain/208/Pioneer_Newspaper%20April%202014%20-%20website.pdf |archive-date=2016-03-13 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>|name="Donnie_R.1"}}，但是仍在測試階段<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.reddit.com/r/Minecraft/comments/3hnxw0/the_very_first_version_of_infdev_in_minecraft/ |title=The Very First Version of Infdev in Minecraft |publisher=Reddit |date=2015-08-20 |accessdate=2016-03-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181013071724/https://www.reddit.com/r/Minecraft/comments/3hnxw0/the_very_first_version_of_infdev_in_minecraft/ |archive-date=2018-10-13 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，最後由於一直無法完成此物件，後來於六月的時候移除了齒輪<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.aminoapps.com/page/minecraft/4381666/removed-feature-cogs | title=Minecraft Removed Feature - Cogs | publisher=aminoapps | accessdate=2016-03-10 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160313202759/http://www.aminoapps.com/page/minecraft/4381666/removed-feature-cogs | archive-date=2016-03-13 | dead-url=yes }}</ref>。在Minecraft遊戲進入下一個開發階段Alpha版發布了之後，泊松辭去工作以全身心投入《Minecraft》開發<ref name="PCGAMERinterview2">{{cite web|last = McDougal|first = Jaz|title = Community heroes: Notch, for ''Minecraft''|url = http://www.pcgamer.com/2010/07/29/community-heroes-notch-for-minecraft/|work = [[PC_Gamer|PC Gamer]]|publisher = [[Future_plc|Future plc]]|accessdate = August 3, 2010|date = July 29, 2010|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20140920035056/http://www.pcgamer.com/2010/07/29/community-heroes-notch-for-minecraft/|archive-date = 2014-09-20|dead-url = no}}</ref>，並用從遊戲中掙來的錢組建了遊戲公司[[Mojang|Mojang]]以支援《Minecraft》的進一步發展<ref name="LackOfUpdates2">{{cite web|last = Persson|first = Markus|authorlink = Markus Persson|publisher = Mojang|title = I'm sorry about the lack of updates|url = http://notch.tumblr.com/post/1205447916/im-sorry-about-the-lack-of-updates|accessdate = October 18, 2010|date = September 28, 2010|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20101004184609/http://notch.tumblr.com/post/1205447916/im-sorry-about-the-lack-of-updates|archive-date = 2010-10-04|dead-url = yes}}</ref><ref name="MCcompany2">{{cite web|last = Persson|first = Markus|authorlink = Markus Persson|publisher = Mojang|title = Hiring some people, getting an office, and all that!|url = http://notch.tumblr.com/post/1075326804/hiring-some-people-getting-an-office-and-all-that|accessdate = September 6, 2010|date = September 6, 2010|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20100908235613/http://notch.tumblr.com/post/1075326804/hiring-some-people-getting-an-office-and-all-that|archive-date = 2010-09-08|dead-url = yes}}</ref>。2010年7月3日，泊松在一次秘密更新中加入了最初的紅石系統<ref name="Donnie_R.1" /><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://notch.tumblr.com/post/763147353/seecret-friday-update-the-third-oooooooooo |title=Seecret Friday update the third! OooooOOOoo! |publisher=The Word of Notch |date=2010-07-03 |accessdate=2016-03-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160314024440/http://notch.tumblr.com/post/763147353/seecret-friday-update-the-third-oooooooooo |archive-date=2016-03-14 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=https://twitter.com/notch/status/17578712007 |title=At birthday party now, the seecret update is coming tonight. It's a beautiful day for a badali. :) |author=[[馬庫斯·阿列克謝·泊松|馬庫斯·阿列克謝·泊松]] |work=[[Twitter|Twitter]] |date=2015-05-18 |access-date=2016-03-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181013071724/https://twitter.com/notch/status/17578712007 |archive-date=2018-10-13 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，加入了包括紅石礦、紅石能量傳輸（紅石粉）、紅石能量源（紅石火把）、簡單電路元件（控制桿、按鈕和壓力板）等紅石元件<ref name="redstonehistory">{{Cite web |url=http://worldofmcmagic.weebly.com/history-of-redstone.html |title=history of redstone |work=worldofmcmagic |accessdate=2016-03-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160313200740/http://worldofmcmagic.weebly.com/history-of-redstone.html |archive-date=2016-03-13 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，此時已經可以完成簡單的邏輯閘，如[[相反閘|相反閘]]<ref>{{cite web | title=Minecraft Redstone Logic | url=http://www.nerdparadise.com/tech/apps/minecraft/redstonelogic/ | publisher=Nerd Paradise | accessdate=2016-01-27 | deadurl=yes | archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160303104736/http://www.nerdparadise.com/tech/apps/minecraft/redstonelogic | archivedate=2016-03-03 }}</ref>，後來遊戲進入下一個開發階段Beta版之後，又陸續加入了一些紅石元件，如活塞<ref name="Gamasutra">{{cite web|url=http://www.gamasutra.com/view/feature/134958/minecraft_intellectual_property_.php3|title=Gamasutra – Minecraft, Intellectual Property, and the Future of Copyright|publisher=|access-date=2016-03-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160310013501/http://www.gamasutra.com/view/feature/134958/minecraft_intellectual_property_.php3|archive-date=2016-03-10|dead-url=no}}</ref>，能接收紅石訊號推動方塊。
此時紅石系統漸漸地變得越來越完整，也開始流行於《Minecraft》文化，許多人利用此系統做出了驚人的東西，如可乘法的電算器甚至做出了電腦。正式版發布之後<ref>{{cite web|archive-url = https://archive.today/20130125195611/http://au.ibtimes.com/articles/251231/20111117/minecraft-version-available-minecon-live-streaming.htm%23.UQLjQn3LdRw|archive-date = 2013-01-25|dead-url = yes|url = http://au.ibtimes.com/articles/251231/20111117/minecraft-version-available-minecon-live-streaming.htm|title = Minecraft Full Version Available; MineCon Live Streaming|work = [[International_Business_Times|International Business Times]]|date = November 17, 2012|accessdate = October 17, 2012|last = Fernandez|first = Carlo}}</ref>，遊戲不斷更新，加入了許多新的遊戲內容<ref name="notchMigr2">{{cite web|title = The web server is struggling, we're migrating|url = http://notch.tumblr.com/post/2812089385/the-web-server-is-struggling-were-migrating|first = Markus|last = Persson|publisher = Mojang|date = January 18, 2011|access-date = 2016-03-12|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20110121031049/http://notch.tumblr.com/post/2812089385/the-web-server-is-struggling-were-migrating|archive-date = 2011-01-21|dead-url = yes}}</ref>。在[[延斯·伯根斯坦|延斯·伯根斯坦]]取代泊松成為遊戲的主要開發者之後<ref name="bergleaddev2">{{cite web|url = http://notch.tumblr.com/post/13633493969/och-med-dom-orden-sa-passar-jag-micken|title = Och med dom orden så passar jag micken|last = Persson|first = Markus|work = [[The_Word_of_Notch|The Word of Notch]]|publisher = Mojang|date = December 2, 2011|accessdate = December 2, 2011|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150106105426/http://notch.tumblr.com/post/13633493969/och-med-dom-orden-sa-passar-jag-micken|archive-date = 2015-01-06|dead-url = yes}}</ref>，在2013年的一次更新之後加入了許多紅石物件，如比較器、一些感應元件和一些主動元件<ref name="mcv-over">{{cite news|url=http://www.mcvnordic.com/news/read/minecon-2012-is-over/0107067|title=MineCon 2012 is over|first=Mats|last=Nylund|date=27 November 2012|work=[[Market_for_Home_Computing_and_Video_Games|Market for Home Computing and Video Games]]|accessdate=28 December 2012|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170922194121/http://www.mcvnordic.com/news/read/MINECON-2012-is-over/0107067|archive-date=2017-09-22|dead-url=yes}}</ref>，後來還加入了能執行命令的方塊<ref name="RPS – 1.3july" />，使紅石系統更為完整，使得玩家能更容易地完成各種[[可程式邏輯裝置|可程式化]]的機關<ref>{{Cite web | url = https://mspoweruser.com/microsoft-planning-bring-command-blocks-minecraft-pocket-edition/ | title = Microsoft Is Planning To Bring Command Blocks And Mods To The Minecraft: Pocket Edition | date = 2016-03-29 | website = MSPoweruser.com | author = Pradeep | access-date = 2019-09-08 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190406213850/https://mspoweruser.com/microsoft-planning-bring-command-blocks-minecraft-pocket-edition/ | archive-date = 2019-04-06 | dead-url = no }}</ref>，也間接促成自定義地圖的興起，間接導致一些沒接觸過Minecraft遊戲的人因為特定主題的自定義地圖而接觸Minecraft遊戲<ref name="Custom maps" />。

後來隨著[[YouTube|YouTube]]媒體網站在《Minecraft》普及的過程中<ref name="Social media">{{cite web | url=http://mashable.com/2010/10/01/minecraft-social-media/ | title=Minecraft: How Social Media Spawned a Gaming Sensation | work=[[Mashable|Mashable]] | publisher=Mashable Inc. | date=2010-10-01 | accessdate=2012-12-28 | last=Silverman | first=Matt | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101003072457/http://mashable.com/2010/10/01/minecraft-social-media/ | archive-date=2010-10-03 | dead-url=no }}</ref>，許多[[YouTube|YouTube]]頻道開始使用Minecraft的紅石介紹一些電路元件，比如[[七段顯示器|七段顯示器]]，逐漸促使紅石又在Minecraft社群中更為流行，部分內容甚至進入流行文化。

== 用於用戶自訂內容 ==

在自定義地圖中，紅石扮演重要的角色，利用紅石實現的邏輯控制，玩家可以建立新的規則、難題甚至包含有任務的自定義地圖<ref name="Custom maps">{{cite web|last=Savage|first=Phil|title=The 25 best Minecraft custom maps|url=http://www.pcgamer.com/2012/10/20/the-25-best-minecraft-custom-maps/|work=[[PC_Gamer|PC Gamer]]|publisher=[[Future_plc|Future plc]]|accessdate=October 28, 2012|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121023211322/http://www.pcgamer.com/2012/10/20/the-25-best-minecraft-custom-maps/|archive-date=2012-10-23|dead-url=no}}</ref>，但早期紅石只有幾種簡單元件要非常複雜的結構才能完成某些操作，但由於自定義地圖的流行，[[Mojang|Mojang]]也對紅石系統做了許多更新，比如直接比較得比較器，還有能用紅石來控制能執行命令的遊戲物件以用更簡單的方式完成更複雜的自定義地圖<ref name="RPS – 1.3july">{{cite web|url=http://www.rockpapershotgun.com/2012/07/06/minecraft-1-3-adding-lan-adventure-mode-in-august/|title=Minecraft 1.3 Adding LAN, Adventure Mode In August|work=[[Rock,_Paper,_Shotgun|Rock, Paper, Shotgun]]|first=Nathan|last=Grayson|date=July 6, 2012|accessdate=January 4, 2013|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121112203224/http://www.rockpapershotgun.com/2012/07/06/minecraft-1-3-adding-lan-adventure-mode-in-august/|archive-date=2012-11-12|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Gallegos">{{cite web|last=Gallegos|first=Anthony|title=Minecraft Adding New Block|url=http://www.ign.com/articles/2012/07/27/minecraft-adding-new-block|work=[[IGN|IGN]]|accessdate=October 28, 2012|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121216094902/http://www.ign.com/articles/2012/07/27/minecraft-adding-new-block|archive-date=2012-12-16|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

=== 遊戲模組 ===
{{main|Minecraft模組}}
早期Minecraft的遊戲模組都要藉由第三方[[軟體|軟體]]修改官方程式來實現遊戲修改，來建立一個與官方Minecraft完全不同的遊戲體驗<ref name="Escapist">{{cite web |url=http://www.escapistmagazine.com/articles/view/video-games/columns/experienced-points/15175-Minecraft-is-Still-A-Thing |title=Yes, Minecraft is Still A Thing |author=Shamus Young |date=28 December 2015 |publisher=Defy Media |work=The Escapist |accessdate=11 February 2016 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180108011831/http://www.escapistmagazine.com/articles/view/video-games/columns/experienced-points/15175-Minecraft-is-Still-A-Thing |archive-date=2018-01-08 |dead-url=no }}</ref>{{#tag:ref|Van Schaik and Vledder 2015<ref name="PUGalacticraft">{{cite book |author = Lars van Schaik and Ronald Vledder |title= De ultieme gids voor Minecraft | url = https://books.google.com/books?id{{=}}4lFqCgAAQBAJ&printsec{{=}}frontcover |year=2015 |publisher=Doetinchem: Reshift Digital |isbn=82-261-0074-7}}</ref>, p. 107|name="PUGalacticraft1"}}，但在2015年9月時出現了利用紅石系統來完成不需修改官方檔案又可以達到遊戲模組的概念<ref>{{cite web | title=Gamemode 4 | url=http://www.gm4.co/gamemode4/ | publisher=gm4.co | accessdate=2016-01-27 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151221033927/http://www.gm4.co/gamemode4/ | archive-date=2015-12-21 | dead-url=no }}</ref>。但由於是利用紅石系統實現，因此需要更複雜的運算，而不如模組直接將代碼改掉而不太需要消耗太多系統資源而沒有取代Minecraft模組在社群中流行的地位<ref name="packtpub history">{{cite web |url=https://www.packtpub.com/books/content/brief-history-minecraft-modding |title=A Brief History of Minecraft Modding |author=Aaron Mills |date=3 June 2015 |publisher= |work=Packt Publishing |accessdate=11 February 2016 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160225042033/https://www.packtpub.com/books/content/brief-history-minecraft-modding |archive-date=2016-02-25 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

== 紅石與[[數位電路|數位邏輯]] ==

遊戲中的紅石可以製成紅石磚塊與紅石火把，他們可以釋放一種叫做紅石能量的能量，粉末紅石可以傳遞這些能量，但是這種能量傳送時會有線性衰減，但紅石火把會因為其他紅石能量輸入而熄滅<ref>{{cite book |author = 王育貞, 張孝謙, 盧品霖 |title= Minecraft（當個創世神）DIY大事典：我的世界: 自己的紅石機關自己做  |year=2016 |publisher=Sharp Point Press |isbn=978-957-10-6411-6 |page=19}}</ref>。利用這個特性就可以做成數位電路<ref name="twvs.tnc">{{cite thesis |url=http://www.shs.edu.tw/works/essay/2015/03/2015030819470013.pdf |title=The Relationship among Minecraft Redstone Circuit and Digital Logic |publisher=[[國立曾文高級農工職業學校|National Tseng-Wen Senior Agricultural & Industrial Vocational School]] |work=Department of Electrical Engineering |first=Yi-Xun |last=Chen |date=March 8, 2015 |accessdate=March 9, 2016 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181013071724/http://www.shs.edu.tw/works/essay/2015/03/2015030819470013.pdf |archive-date=2018-10-13 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，數位電路中的訊號有高電位1、低電位0、中間值x和高阻抗z，紅石的磚塊與紅石的火把可以做為高電位1的訊號原、熄滅的紅石火把、衰減至零的紅石訊號、沒有接紅石源的可以作為低電位0<ref>{{Cite web | url = https://www.wired.com/2010/10/virtual-computers/ | title = Geeky Gamers Build Working Computers out of Virtual Blocks | author = Priya Ganapati | date = 2010-10-12 | website = wired.com | access-date = 2019-09-08 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20140524025808/http://www.wired.com/2010/10/virtual-computers | archive-date = 2014-05-24 | dead-url = no }}</ref>，紅石線相接可以傳遞訊號也可以做出中間值x和高阻抗z，即實現三態邏輯電路{{#tag:ref|Tom Peerdeman. UVA 2014<ref name="Tom_Peerdeman_UVA">{{cite web |url=https://esc.fnwi.uva.nl/thesis/centraal/files/f1408977246.pdf |title=Minecraft to C for the Raspberry Pi |publisher=[[阿姆斯特丹大學|Universiteit Van Amsterdam]] |author=Tom Peerdeman |date=July 1, 2014 |accessdate=March 9, 2016 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181013071725/https://esc.fnwi.uva.nl/thesis/centraal/files/f1408977246.pdf |archive-date=2018-10-13 |dead-url=no }}</ref>, chapter 2. Overview of the redstone components|name="Tom_Peerdeman_UVA1"}}。

=== 硬體描述語言 ===
{{main|硬體描述語言}}
由於Minecraft的紅石系統也可以被設計得十分複雜，因此在社群中也發展出了關於紅石電路的[[電子設計自動化|邏輯電路設計自動化]]相關工具及腳本，甚至有專門用於描述Minecraft的紅石系統的硬體描述語言<ref>{{cite web |url=https://github.com/kkroening/RedGen |title=RedGen -- a tool that automates the process of constructing redstone circuits in Minecraft. |author=kkroening |date=2014-06-07 |publisher=github |accessdate=2016-03-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180611003902/https://github.com/kkroening/RedGen |archive-date=2018-06-11 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，甚至也有試圖直接將描述、設計電子系統、數位電路的[[硬體描述語言|硬體描述語言]]--Verilog{{#tag:ref| Zainalabedin Navabi 2007<ref name="Navabi0">{{cite book|author=Zainalabedin Navabi|title=Verilog数字系统设计——RTL综合、测试平台与验证（第二版）（英文名：Verilog Digital System Design: Register Transfer Level Synthesis, Testbench, and Verification, Second Edition）|publisher=电子工业出版社|isbn=978-7-121-04767-1}}</ref>, p. 3-7|name="Navabi"}}<ref name="nguyen2016pershing">{{Cite paper|url=https://www.ocf.berkeley.edu/~qmn/assets/nguyen_pershing_2016.pdf|title=PERSHING: An Automatic Place-and-Route Tool for Minecraft Redstone Circuits | author=Nguyen, Quan | year=2016}}</ref>直接編譯成Minecraft物件的專案<ref>{{cite web | title=MCVerilog - A Verilog to Minecraft Compiler | url=http://devpost.com/software/mcverilog | publisher=devpost | accessdate=2016-01-27 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160313202104/http://devpost.com/software/mcverilog | archive-date=2016-03-13 | dead-url=no }}</ref>，但是這類專案發展到一半就都沒有下文了。比較知名的紅石設計者多半沒有靠這類工具就直接做出了文字顯示器，甚至還試圖將處理器、ALU、CPU還有RAM都做出來<ref>{{cite web | title=Minecraft player creates word processor out of redstone | url=http://www.pcgamer.com/minecraft-player-creates-word-processor-out-of-redstone/ | publisher=pcgamer | date=2015-01-07 | accessdate=2016-01-27 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160123233004/http://www.pcgamer.com/minecraft-player-creates-word-processor-out-of-redstone/ | archive-date=2016-01-23 | dead-url=no }}</ref>。

== 影響 ==

由於Minecraft的流行，再加上紅石系統比現實數位邏輯電路來的簡單，因此Minecraft的紅石電路是讓孩子們開始電路或數位邏輯的一個網關<ref name="verge">{{cite web|url=http://www.theverge.com/2014/9/15/6152085/why-parents-love-minecraft|title=Why parents are raising their kids on Minecraft|author=Ben Popper|date=15 September 2014|publisher=Vox Media|work=The Verge|access-date=2016-03-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160310074819/http://www.theverge.com/2014/9/15/6152085/why-parents-love-minecraft|archive-date=2016-03-10|dead-url=no}}</ref>，經常被用作於電子學與數位邏輯電路的入門教材<ref name="learn">{{cite web | title=Minecraft Circuits in Real Life | url=http://solderingsunday.com/minecraft-circuits-in-real-life-4/ | publisher=solderingsunday | accessdate=2016-01-27 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160313203342/http://solderingsunday.com/minecraft-circuits-in-real-life-4/ | archive-date=2016-03-13 | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web | url = https://www.cnet.com/special-reports/minecraft/mindcraft-helping-students-learn/ | title = Minecraft in the classroom | website = cnet.com | date = 2016-03-30 | author = Stephen Shankland | access-date = 2019-09-08 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190903123227/https://www.cnet.com/special-reports/minecraft/mindcraft-helping-students-learn/ | archive-date = 2019-09-03 | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref name="npr.org"/>，甚至還有發行電路紅石實驗包使初學者能利用Minecraft的紅石概念更簡單的學習使用[[麵包板|麵包板]]和電路板。有時甚至會將Minecraft作為再製作物理測試前測試電子產品的好方法<ref>{{cite web | title=Learning Logic Gates with Minecraft | author=popewill | url=http://www.instructables.com/id/Learning-Logic-Gates-with-Minecraft/ | publisher=instructables | date=2015-01-07 | accessdate=2016-01-27 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160313201355/http://www.instructables.com/id/Learning-Logic-Gates-with-Minecraft/ | archive-date=2016-03-13 | dead-url=no }}</ref>。紅石系統不只是Minecraft遊戲內容，也讓許多沒接觸過電子學的人學習了數位邏輯與電子電路<ref>{{cite web |url=http://anyelse.cc/article/49764.html |title=吐血推薦，學生黨必看！玩這幾款遊戲時，別人問起來可以說「我在學習」 |publisher=anyelse.cc |author=张敏 |date=2015-08-06 |accessdate=2016-03-09 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160313202627/http://anyelse.cc/article/49764.html |archivedate=2016-03-13 }}</ref>。

搭配模組後紅石系統可以變得更強大，紅石線路可以更簡單，因此更適合作為教學用途，例如ComputerCraftEdu專案採用了2011的ComputerCraft模組內的電腦與紅石擴充作為教育目的<ref name="GamasutraTeaching">{{cite web|url=http://gamasutra.com/view/news/247888/TeacherGaming_mods_Minecraft_to_teach_basic_coding_skills.php|title=Gamasutra – TeacherGaming mods Minecraft to teach basic coding skills|author=Alex Wawro|publisher=|access-date=2016-03-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160310003156/http://gamasutra.com/view/news/247888/TeacherGaming_mods_Minecraft_to_teach_basic_coding_skills.php|archive-date=2016-03-10|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

